{"article_id":"LKfZkJUDKr3TaQl8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Obama ,","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"under fire for the rocky debut of his signature health care program ,","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"shifted gears Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to focus on the economy","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and reiterate his call for an increase in the minimum wage .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"\" It will be good for our economy ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"it will be good for our families , \"","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Obama said of a minimum wage hike .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"The White House is backing a bill","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that would raise the federal minimum to just over $ 10 an hour , up from $ 7.25 .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Critics of a minimum wage increase argue","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"that it could have the perverse effect","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"of hurting the economy ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"resulting in higher costs for consumers and fewer jobs","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"to offset the cost of higher wages .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"But Obama touted local efforts","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"to address the minimum wage .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Around the same time as Obama ' s speech , the D.C. Council voted to give preliminary approval","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"to hike the minimum wage to $ 11.50 an hour ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"which would be one of the nation 's highest .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The president called the growing income gap a `` defining challenge of our time . ''","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"`` The basic bargain at the heart of our economy has frayed , ''","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"the president said in remarks at a nonprofit community center a short drive from the White House in one of Washington 's most impoverished neighborhoods .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"He was also in friendly territory , at an event","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"sponsored by the Center for American Progress , a think tank with close ties to the White House .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"The president vowed to focus the last three years of his presidency on addressing the discrepancy and a rapidly growing deficit of opportunity","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"he said","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"is a bigger threat than the fiscal deficit .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"But Sen. Jeff Sessions , R-Ala. , argued","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"that the president 's message was undermined by his support for an immigration overhaul","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"which","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"he claimed","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"would hurt workers .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"\" It is shocking for the President to give a speech about income disparity and falling wages","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"while pushing an immigration plan","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that will hammer American workers","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and widen the disparity , ''","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"he said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"Obama 's remarks on the economy come","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"as he seeks to move past the health care woes","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"that have consumed his presidency in recent months .","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"He acknowledged his administration 's `` poor execution ''","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"in rolling out the flawed website","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"that was supposed to be an easy portal","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"for purchasing insurance ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"while blaming Republicans for a `` reckless '' partial shutdown of the government .","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"`` Nobody has acquitted themselves very well these past few months .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"So it 's not surprising that the American people 's frustrations with Washington are at an all-time high , ''","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Obama said .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"But he added","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"that Americans ' frustrations also run high","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"to try to meet ends meet ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"no matter how hard they work .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"The speech comes amid growing national and international attention to economic disparities","depth":4},{"id":55,"text":"-- from the writings of Pope Francis to the protests of fast-food workers in the U.S .","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"The president cited the pope 's question","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"of how it is n't news","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"when an elderly homeless person dies from exposure ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"but news","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"when stock market loses two points .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Obama said","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"increasing income inequality is more pronounced in the United States than other countries .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"Americans should be offended","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that a child","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"born into poverty","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"has such a hard time","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"escaping it .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"`` It should compel us to action .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"We 're a better country than this , ''","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"the president said .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Obama did not propose any new policy initiatives in the speech .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":145,"left":126,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":111,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":92,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":87,"right":91,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":87,"left":82,"right":86,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":77,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":75,"right":76,"relation":"purpose","nu